Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.41,0:00:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1500)\pos(424,430)}{\1a&H50&\2a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\be1\b0\fs-4}{\K100}献给曾经喜爱这世界的人们\N\N{\K200}{\K150}曾经与这世界的同伴欢度时光的人们\N\N{\K250}{\K150}呈现给这重逢的此刻——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tseng
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  总之快一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reno  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那是谁?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elena
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Life Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是围绕着星球的生命之河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球和生息在星球上所有生物的生命源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神罗公司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了把Life Stream当作能源使用的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了它  使我们的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变的非常富裕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有很多人认为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种方法会导致星球的毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神罗对于反对他的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用武力镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神罗拥有被称作Soldier的特别士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:04:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs-3}Soldier：神罗公司治安维持部门的最强部队对其所属人员的称呼。\N由强至弱共分1st、2nd、3rd三个等级。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被移植了很久以前从天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企图毁灭这个星球带来灾厄的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JENOVA的细胞的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他们之中有一个叫Sephiroth的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常优秀的Soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在他获知自己是由如此可怕的实验而诞生的事实之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从此开始憎恨神罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不知何时  他开始憎恨这一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神罗  以及反神罗的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于过度憎恨  连星球都想破坏的Sephiroth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和全力阻止Sephiroth的人们之间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了无数次的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数的战斗也伴随着无数的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢的人也化成了Life Stream的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后在那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运之日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终结这一切战争的是星球自身的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球把Life Stream当作武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涌现到地面的Life Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的争斗  野心  悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统统吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以悲伤换来这一切  全部都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的说法是从两年前开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这个星球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我们所想像的要更加更加愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕综合症
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  Marlene
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要把Denzel带走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不在了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  这里是冲击货运公司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs-3}The Strike Life Delivery Service
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本公司什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是哪一位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reno从Healin打电话过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是有工作要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud  还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留言结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj  那就是哥哥的城市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想他会欢迎我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别哭噢  Yazoo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别哭啊  Loz
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  哥哥来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哥哥你藏了起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你在骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然妈妈还是在你那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想跟你浪费唇舌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我接社长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  Barret  成功了  我找到新的油田了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油  田  那可真大的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作差不多完了  再过不久就要去见Marlene了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我问候一下  回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reno又打电话来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说很紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得有点奇怪  当心一点噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你厉害  服了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷啊  Rude
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是曾经自称Soldier的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来功夫没有退步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Rufus？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是倒楣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天  我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大厦倒塌时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击我的人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是保住一命…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们神罗欠世界一笔很大的债务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把世界搞成这副凄惨模样的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被说是我们引起的也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  无论如何也要还清这笔帐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开始针对Sephiroth所留下的影响展开调查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在北方的大空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜发现了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以放心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  发生了令人出乎意料之外的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人阻挠我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Kadaj一行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目的好像就是要阻止我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  真不知道他们在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会被袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我们的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj一行既年轻又残暴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们的结论要是雇用一名身手非凡的保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作是送货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你没有其他人选
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  原Soldier  Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我自称的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"妈妈"是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj说了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这年头  怀念母亲的小孩多的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你跟孤儿们住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让那些孩子们重拾笑容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的最终目的  是重建一个新的世界  Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦  Cloud  重建神罗公司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reno
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud住在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Denzel一样  Cloud也生病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为生病才离家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他准备一个人去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本不打算战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧  Marlene
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我想见Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见面以后要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前得好好说他一顿是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  下次我会实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那似乎是在摆脱你们的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从直升机上掉了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很蠢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我发誓也行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就向这个发誓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要妈妈的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再结成时必须要用到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:18:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再结成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs-3}ReUnion：再结成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让拥有妈妈细胞的伙伴们再次齐聚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后向这星球复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然准备的很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有人把妈妈给藏了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长你也很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是多亏在Life Stream里面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈遗传思念的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却连妈妈在哪都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很惭愧  但这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们只不过是思念体而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找到妈妈赋予我们细胞为止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是变不回原样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有思念和星痕还是不够完美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以为了真正的结合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:20:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长  你早就发觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会连你的份也好好活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想当Soldier？ 加油噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了Midgar  你有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.39,0:22:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你  妈妈在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来可以大玩一场了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.10,0:24:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.77,0:24:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.24,0:24:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.71,0:24:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把她带走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.18,0:24:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.10,0:25:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.44,0:25:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.32,0:25:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有星痕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.46,0:25:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能治好你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.81,0:26:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.38,0:26:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.52,0:26:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来得太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.99,0:26:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.76,0:26:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.20,0:27:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marlene
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.17,0:27:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.51,0:28:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.25,0:28:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和孩子们住在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.02,0:28:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却没半个人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.86,0:28:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不担心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.70,0:28:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.61,0:28:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.27,0:29:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥藏了起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.03,0:29:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由Life Stream诞生的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.17,0:29:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这魔石将赐与我们新的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.30,0:29:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reno他们出去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.81,0:29:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是星痕综合症吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.88,0:30:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得就这样死去也无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.22,0:30:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.65,0:30:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有治疗方法
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.69,0:30:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  Denzel很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.16,0:30:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逃避  要不要一起战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.50,0:30:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家互相帮助  一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.90,0:30:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为不是真正的家人  才不愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.14,0:30:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.04,0:30:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也救不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.51,0:30:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是家人  或是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.35,0:30:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.69,0:30:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖拖拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.56,0:30:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.50,0:30:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要拖到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.70,0:30:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没找到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.60,0:31:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有目击者看到是他们带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.87,0:31:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.25,0:31:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗忘之都
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.31,0:31:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏匿处
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.20,0:31:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从妈妈那里得到了特殊的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.20,0:31:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赋予人类痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.33,0:31:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及与这星球战斗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.84,0:31:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这种力量大家也都拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.78,0:31:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.08,0:31:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们都是兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.45,0:31:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承了融合在Life Stream里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.12,0:31:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被选上继承妈妈遗传思念的兄弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.99,0:31:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.96,0:32:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这星球正阻挠着大家
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.66,0:32:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正打算阻止我们的成长
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.94,0:32:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们的身体会感到疼痛  内心会受到挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.74,0:32:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会治好你们
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.71,0:32:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后到妈妈的身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.48,0:32:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们家族齐心合力  一起向这星球复仇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.83,0:32:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.67,0:33:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denzel
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.25,0:33:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denzel
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.16,0:34:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.96,0:34:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己都快撑不住了  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.36,0:34:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会好转的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.93,0:34:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.42,0:34:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要来这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.47,0:34:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  想得到原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.45,0:34:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想得到原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.87,0:34:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.93,0:35:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.68,0:35:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接孩子们回家
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.10,0:35:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人啊  是我们的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.09,0:35:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  很可惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.45,0:35:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.69,0:35:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.68,0:38:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的都无法得救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.50,0:38:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vincent  到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.39,0:38:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.85,0:38:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以看到了Kadaj的事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.07,0:38:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.05,0:38:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有能排除侵入体内异分子扩散的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.82,0:38:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体内也会有像Life Stream的结构
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.84,0:38:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此会跟入侵体内的邪恶分子对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.44,0:38:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶分子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.87,0:38:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sephiroth因子  JENOVA的遗传思念
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.22,0:38:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎么称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.69,0:38:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的很详细啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.81,0:38:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tseng和Elena
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.81,0:38:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奄奄一息的状态下被带来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.24,0:39:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了不少残酷的拷问
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.71,0:39:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然救了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.70,0:39:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.67,0:39:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拷问
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.37,0:39:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.92,0:39:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们似乎把JENOVA的人头弄到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.00,0:39:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj所寻找的妈妈就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.12,0:39:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从天而降的凶神
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.41,0:39:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JENOVA
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.93,0:39:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他们愿意  就可以再次创造出一个Sephiroth
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.75,0:39:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.86,0:39:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.57,0:39:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.83,0:39:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marlene
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.89,0:39:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud  Denzel他？ Tifa她？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.37,0:39:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa没事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.87,0:39:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见Tifa
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.16,0:39:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.34,0:40:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.15,0:40:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vincent  能不能把Marlene送回店里
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.78,0:40:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找神罗他们
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.82,0:40:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不赞成这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.83,0:40:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.61,0:40:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.92,0:40:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你就不肯听我们的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.99,0:40:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marlene
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.68,0:40:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.43,0:40:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想战斗马上就会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.68,0:40:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  光只战斗是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.95,0:40:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.74,0:40:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.29,0:40:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud  你打算开战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.74,0:40:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.89,0:40:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗忘之都
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.91,0:40:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏匿处
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.77,0:40:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.72,0:40:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟Rufus谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.28,0:40:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.53,0:40:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.67,0:41:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算找到孩子们可能也无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.46,0:41:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能会造成无法挽回的后果
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.09,0:41:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕会变成这样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.42,0:41:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在你应该接受更多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.22,0:41:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很沉重吗  因为那沉重到无法承受
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.31,0:41:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得要一个人来你才能忍下去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.91,0:41:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很厌恶孤单对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.36,0:41:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不肯接电话却死抓着不放
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.94,0:41:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去藏匿处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.08,0:41:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们输给了回忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.65,0:41:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我曾经视而不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.07,0:41:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是拖拖拉拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.92,0:41:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.23,0:41:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候原谅自己了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.42,0:42:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过错…  能被原谅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.01,0:42:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没试过
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.77,0:42:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝试？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.87,0:42:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.02,0:42:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marlene  我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.98,0:42:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.15,0:42:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我会通知你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.60,0:42:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是里布  工作的怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.57,0:42:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看过广告了  但那东西真能赚钱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.05,0:42:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那很适合Cloud先生就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.70,0:42:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话我也想帮忙  所以再连络
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.10,0:42:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reno从Healin打电话来  说是有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.84,0:42:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见  是我  Yuffie
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.14,0:43:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wutai的孩子们都不见了  你知道是怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.81,0:43:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道些事情的话  拜托你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.21,0:43:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,样子有点奇怪  当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.84,0:43:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从不觉得你有对不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.49,0:43:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是来了吗  这样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.92,0:44:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.42,0:44:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.80,0:44:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denzel
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.37,0:44:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denzel
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.64,0:45:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denzel
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.73,0:45:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.24,0:45:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈就在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.65,0:45:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.05,0:45:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫什么纪念碑的  是神罗建的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.39,0:45:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  还会动头脑耶
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.02,0:45:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你们猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.18,0:45:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.34,0:45:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.24,0:46:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.19,0:46:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  Kadaj
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.31,0:46:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.10,0:46:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一件噢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.48,0:46:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过  只要弄到JENOVA的细胞就能恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.14,0:46:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.47,0:46:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"他"将会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.96,0:46:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sephiroth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.99,0:46:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.88,0:46:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.26,0:46:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.84,0:46:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道Sephiroth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.27,0:46:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有感觉到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.69,0:46:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我感到急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.39,0:46:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈是会选择我  还是Sephiroth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.32,0:46:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的思念体
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.99,0:47:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论如何你们的结果都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.13,0:47:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈是经过了漫长的旅途才来到这星球
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.14,0:47:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了将愚蠢的事物从宇宙中消除
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.11,0:47:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.95,0:47:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里和妈妈到来时一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.48,0:47:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想让妈妈高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.44,0:47:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是妈妈的命令我什么都干
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.06,0:47:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  重演恶梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.89,0:47:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你们在  不管什么事都会一而再的重复
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.10,0:47:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围绕着星球的Life Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.37,0:47:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断在生死之间来回
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.04,0:47:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说那轮回才是生命的原型的话
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.34,0:47:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重蹈覆辙的历史就是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.93,0:47:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是JENOVA还是Sephiroth
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.14,0:47:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就随你们喜欢做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.49,0:48:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会听从命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.69,0:48:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会一次又一次的阻止你们
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.76,0:48:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长  这就是你们抢走妈妈的藉口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.23,0:48:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你该不会是很后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.27,0:48:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔？ 我可是快乐的不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.49,0:48:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  那么差不多也该结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.54,0:49:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denzel  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.36,0:50:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.80,0:50:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.04,0:50:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.70,0:51:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.31,0:51:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.15,0:51:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.98,0:51:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快个头！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.86,0:51:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们太顽固了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.46,0:52:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗  只要把妈妈交出来这一切就都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.27,0:52:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.85,0:52:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用JENOVA的头想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.29,0:52:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再结成什么的  是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.46,0:52:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只不过是想见妈妈而已
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.67,0:52:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈将会决定今后的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.20,0:52:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.28,0:53:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈妈妈的  还不就是JENOVA而已
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.86,0:53:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.93,0:53:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许你这样说妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.96,0:53:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.33,0:53:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.77,0:53:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…  干嘛要道歉啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.99,0:54:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.30,0:54:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.14,0:54:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这照顾妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.05,0:54:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Barret
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.55,0:54:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marlene没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.10,0:54:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.83,0:55:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁用了我的魔石？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.80,0:55:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.54,0:55:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.04,0:55:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.62,0:55:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的Sierra号
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.06,0:55:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会让你上去坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.56,0:55:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯行在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.13,0:55:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.30,0:55:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.71,0:56:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marlene没事  我把她放在店里了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.98,0:56:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.88,0:56:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得轻松了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.05,0:56:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.39,0:56:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是拖拖拉拉的时候磨轻了的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.03,0:56:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.90,0:56:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Marlene一起等着
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.30,0:56:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud也会回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.29,0:58:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.89,0:59:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太愉快了  社长  接下来再召唤什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.69,0:59:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.70,1:00:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不肖子  该早点发现啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.12,1:00:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  Cloud
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.42,1:00:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一把
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.08,1:00:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.30,1:00:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.33,1:00:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.02,1:01:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.21,1:01:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.06,1:02:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.90,1:02:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.08,1:06:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说搭档
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.05,1:06:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  很厉害吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.09,1:06:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合了神罗的技术制作
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.59,1:07:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你做的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.10,1:07:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说威力  漂亮的很
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.97,1:07:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇噢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.37,1:07:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢吧  搭挡
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.52,1:07:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来今天不必加班了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.05,1:08:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.80,1:08:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.23,1:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.27,1:10:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  Cloud
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.20,1:11:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于见到妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.32,1:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要如何开始
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.81,1:11:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈会告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.82,1:11:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念体什么都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.54,1:11:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我只不过是个被操纵的玩偶
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.87,1:11:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和以前的你
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.66,1:11:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.66,1:12:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud  我拿魔石来了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.43,1:12:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摇啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.63,1:12:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  Cid  快点降下去
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.34,1:12:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  想下去自己跳下去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.60,1:12:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让他一个人战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.15,1:12:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.77,1:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是Sephiroth的思念体
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.97,1:12:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是幼虫一样
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.04,1:12:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼虫？ 虫子？ 那家伙是虫子？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.45,1:12:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  别激动
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.08,1:12:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会变成Sephiroth吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.35,1:12:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud知道吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.89,1:12:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.53,1:12:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.34,1:12:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让他一个人战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.77,1:12:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白  谁来说明一下
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.76,1:12:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人才会知道
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.22,1:12:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差别待遇  差别待遇!!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.18,1:12:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别激动  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.33,1:12:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人也不懂
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.43,1:12:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年前
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.26,1:12:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最后一战时确实拥有坚强的心
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.65,1:12:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但两年的时光却让他遗忘了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.92,1:13:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  Cloud是想找回那心情
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.14,1:13:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呿  那就等他十分钟吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.66,1:13:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud还是一样那么难伺候
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.27,1:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫正直
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.71,1:14:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你见识见识  我的再结成
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.69,1:14:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了  Cloud
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.02,1:15:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕没有了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.96,1:15:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.67,1:15:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底期望什么
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.77,1:15:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依宿星痕上死者的思念
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.50,1:15:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和Life Stream一起围绕着星球
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.30,1:15:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天开始侵蚀星球
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.80,1:15:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud  我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.38,1:15:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是把这颗星球当作方舟  在黑暗的宇宙中旅行
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.78,1:15:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像妈妈过去所作的一样
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.82,1:15:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我们会找到新的星球
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.26,1:15:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且在新的天地创造光辉的未来
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.60,1:15:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个星球会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.77,1:16:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晓得  接下来就要看你了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.89,1:16:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.01,1:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么让你变强的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.47,1:17:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.53,1:17:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直考虑该送什么给你
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.15,1:18:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你"绝望"如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.36,1:18:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪下吧  让我看看你请求饶恕的模样
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.65,1:19:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最重要的东西是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.05,1:20:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我享受将它从你身边夺走的喜悦吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.17,1:20:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲  你什么都不明白
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.18,1:20:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有什么不重要的事物
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.39,1:20:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回忆中安息吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.01,1:20:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.58,1:21:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会成为回忆的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.56,1:21:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.26,1:21:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.91,1:21:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.21,1:21:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经很努力了  放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.93,1:22:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…  妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.79,1:22:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到大家的身边吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.87,1:22:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.66,1:23:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他成功了  我就知道它一定行
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.15,1:23:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  我说得没错吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.67,1:23:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉  Cloud真是个男子汉
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.93,1:23:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud一定能办到
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.93,1:23:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好好抓紧啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.25,1:23:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直…  都在我们身边吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.27,1:23:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.95,1:24:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.03,1:24:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…  一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.18,1:25:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.49,1:25:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud  会回来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.72,1:26:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.66,1:26:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.06,1:26:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他第几次叫我妈妈啦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.71,1:26:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么思念你  又有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.26,1:26:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要这么大的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.44,1:26:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜  看来这里没有你待的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.88,1:27:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.47,1:27:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说Cloud会来这里
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.07,1:27:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你回来
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.43,1:27:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.27,1:27:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有星痕没消失的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.84,1:27:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.79,1:27:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  把它治好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.87,1:28:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.48,1:28:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.54,1:29:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  尽管跳下去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.39,1:29:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了治好了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.93,1:29:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.59,1:30:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.15,1:30:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.41,1:30:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是一个人了